  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\nIf you receive a mention in an edit (original message was normal, then edited to have a mention), the badge will not appear or get updated.\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\n1. Open account A\r\n2. Send a normal message to a community shared with account A with account B\r\n3. Edit the message to mention account A with account B\r\n4. See in account A that there is no badge\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nThe badge for mentions appears (or increments if it was already there)\r\n\r\n\r\n",
